parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to lose acceleration, jerk, or slip, leading to a hazardous situation, especially when driving in heavy traffic or attempting to turn through cross-traffic. This can increase the risk of accidents and put the occupants' lives at stake.
symptoms: The vehicle loses acceleration
jerks
or slips while driving
the transmission makes a whining noise
the vehicle vibrates or shakes upon acceleration
the transmission fails to engage
the vehicle is unable to move forward or backward
the vehicle's speed is limited to 5-10 mph.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The CVT transmission slipping or jerking can cause the vehicle to lose acceleration, leading to a hazardous situation, especially when driving in heavy traffic or attempting to turn through cross-traffic. This can increase the risk of accidents and put the occupants' lives at stake.
symptoms: The transmission slips or jerks while driving
the vehicle loses acceleration
the transmission makes a whining noise
the vehicle vibrates or shakes upon acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The complete failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to become immobile, leaving the occupants stranded and at risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission fails to engage
the vehicle is unable to move forward or backward
the vehicle's speed is limited to 5-10 mph.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling off of paint on the hood and rear lift door can lead to corrosion and damage to the underlying metal surface, affecting the vehicle's appearance and potentially compromising its structural integrity.
symptoms: Paint peeling off
exposing primed or metal surface
usually on the hood and rear lift door.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Rear Passenger Side Door Sensor
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear passenger side door sensor can cause the door to close on a person, potentially causing injury, especially to children.
symptoms: The rear passenger side door fails to retract on time
despite detecting an object or person in its path.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Tire Wear on Toyo A22 Tires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive tire wear can lead to reduced traction, increased stopping distances, and a higher risk of accidents, particularly in wet weather conditions.
symptoms: Premature wear on the outside edges of the front tires
bald spots on the outside edge of the tires
uneven tire wear
reduced traction in wet weather.
